'''Yousif B. Aljamal Jr.''' (born in [[Pampanga]] on June 14, 1983) is a Filipino former [[professional sports|professional]] [[basketball]] player who last played for the [[GlobalPort Batang Pier]] in the [[Philippine Basketball Association]] (PBA). He is also a former [[National Collegiate Athletic Association (Philippines)|NCAA]] Most Valuable Player for its 82nd season with the [[San Beda Red Lions]].
